node.text:
Very tired of politicians giving impassioned speeches followed by no action. So with that in mind I just formally requested the U.S. Cabinet invoke the 25th Amendment. This can work, we just need the public outcry to be deafening. Call your senators and member of congress (dem and GOP) and demand they do the same. 

Joe Biden does not simply have a pattern of poor decision making – his mental decline is on full display.

We must not allow this mentally unstable individual to direct our country one second longer.

node.title: If the Taliban harm the Americans there will be vengeance

node.text:
Evening thoughts. Don’t vote for someone who makes you feel good, vote for will actually DO good. The idea that any middle eastern group has our weaponry is infuriating. No one can be this inept, this has to be on purpose. Seems like our dementia patient just wants to give our tanks, black hawks, and drones to China for them to study, albeit by proxy. 

To our enemies: the levers of power will be in strong hands soon enough, and if you attack America or our interests under this weak president, we will not forget. We are in the business of hunting down and killing terrorist. There is no where on this earth you can hide from us. Remember that.

node.title: The game of of politics is much different from governing.

This can work, we just need the public outcry to be deafening. Call your senators and member of congress (dem and GOP) and demand they do the same. 

Joe Biden does not simply have a pattern of poor decision making – his mental decline is on full display.

We must not allow this mentally unstable individual to direct our country one second longer.

Evening thoughts. Don’t vote for someone who makes you feel good, vote for will actually DO good. The idea that any middle eastern group has our weaponry is infuriating. No one can be this inept, this has to be on purpose. Seems like our dementia patient just wants to give our tanks, black hawks, and drones to China for them to study, albeit by proxy. 

To our enemies: the levers of power will be in strong hands soon enough, and if you attack America or our interests under this weak president, we will not forget. We are in the business of hunting down and killing terrorist. There is no where on this earth you can hide from us. Remember that.
